Package org.jetel.graph.analyse

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EdgeFunction
    This class defines transitional function from a component to an other component.
    GraphProvider
    This interface is primarily dedicated for GraphCycleInspector class.
    InspectedComponent
    This interface is used by GraphCycleInspector for graph layout tracking.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractGraphProvider
    Common ancestor for both implementation of GraphProvider interface.
    AbstractInspectedComponent
    Abstract implementation of InspectedComponent.
    BasicInspectedComponent
    Component wrapper for basic graph.
    EdgeFunctionImpl  
    FastPropagateSubgraphInspector
    This class is used to inspect subgraphs and makes all edges interconnecting SubgraphInput and SubgraphOutput components with fast propagating variant of edge types.
    GraphCycleInspector
    This is graph cycle detector.
    LoopsInspector
    This class is used to inspect graphs with Loop components and all edges on the loop are converted to fast-propagate type.
    SingleGraphProvider
    This class is used by GraphCycleInspector class to provide all components of inspected graph.
